The powers of a workplace inspector under that section may only be exercised: 



 "169(1) (a) for the purpose of determining whether any of the following are being, or have been, observed: 
 (i) workplace agreements; 
 (ii) awards; 
 ..." 





7 It is submitted that, at least by 2 February 2007, a decision had been made to commence the current proceedings alleging contravention of the terms of the relevant certified (workplace) agreement.
